title: 113: Awkward Conversations with Teens ft. Mayim Bialik | Ear Biscuits Ep. 113
description:
Rhett & Link are joined by Mayim Bialik, actress, neuroscientist, author, and Buddy System Season 2 cast member, to talk her book Girling Up, growing up in the industry, parenting almost teens, and more on this week's Ear Biscuits.

Get more from Mayim here:

Girling Up: https://www.amazon.com/Girling-Up-Strong-Smart-Spectacular/dp/0399548602
